title: Capstone Project
text: She and her team developed a dynamic, web-based information management system for Barangay Olympia, Makati City, using PHP (Laravel Framework), MySQL, HTML, CSS, Bootstrap 5.3v, JavaScript, jQuery, AJAX, SweetAlert, FullCalendar, and Boxicons. As the frontend developer, she was responsible for designing and developing the user interface, ensuring it was user-friendly and efficient. As a QA tester, she performed manual testing to identify bugs, ensuring the functionality of the system and maintaining high-quality standards for both the frontend and backend. Since the system is dynamic in nature, it consists of 48 tables.
